# `.pen` files in `design-system/`

- Use **Pencil MCP** to read and modify design content (`batch_get`, `batch_design`, `open_document`, `get_screenshot`, `export_nodes` as needed).
- After changes, run **`pnpm run validate:pen-files`** from the repo root.
- Follow node naming and token usage described in `/design-system/README.md` and `/docs/architecture/business/design-system/pen-files-guide.md`.
